room_title: Escape room "Survivors vs Survivors" by Lights Out Escape Rooms in Denver
room_address: 1500 W Littleton Blvd Unit 110 C/D Littleton, CO 80120
room_description: It has been a year since the zombie outbreak. Your group of survivors has decided that they can no longer go on without additional support. There is a nearby community that is willing to take in some new members. In order to get in though, the community leader is requiring a tribute. You must scavenge a nearby house in order to find the necessary resources.
